code: @Override protected IndexFieldData.XFieldComparatorSource createFieldComparator(String fieldName, MultiValueMode sortMode, Object missingValue, Nested nested) {     IndexNumericFieldData fieldData = getForField(fieldName).     return new LongValuesComparatorSource(fieldData, missingValue, sortMode, nested). }
@Override protected IndexableField createField(String name, int value) {     return new SortedNumericDocValuesField(name, value). }
